@startuml 购物与配送时序图
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #1565C0

actor 买家 as Buyer
actor 卖家 as Seller
participant "前端" as Front
participant "后端 API" as API
participant "数据库" as DB

== 1. 买家下单 ==
Buyer -> Front : 点击“立即购买”
Front -> API : POST /api/orders\n{product_id, quantity}
API -> DB : INSERT INTO orders
DB --> API : 订单创建成功
API --> Front : {order_id, status: "paid"}
Front --> Buyer : 显示订单详情

== 2. 卖家出货 ==
Seller -> Front : 进入订单管理，点“发货”
Front -> API : PUT /api/orders/{id}\n{status: "shipped"}
API -> DB : UPDATE orders SET status='shipped'
DB --> API : 更新成功
API --> Front : {order_id, status: "shipped"}
Front --> Seller : 提示“出货成功”

== 3. 买家收货 ==
Buyer -> Front : 确认收货
Front -> API : PUT /api/orders/{id}\n{status: "received"}
API -> DB : UPDATE orders SET status='received'
DB --> API : 更新成功
API --> Front : {order_id, status: "received"}
Front --> Buyer : 交易完成
@enduml